  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discord Community Server</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617480/extras/1100fe509dec59f51538d1894249998a.avif?t=1627283233\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br>Whether it’s playing around or having a full-on competition, Fight party’s random map generation and weapons allows for a new battle to occur every round. Have a refreshed experience every round or pick and choose between what weapons you’d like to spawn.<br>However there can only be one winner.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 - 8 player split-screen multiplayer<br></li><li> Random items<br></li><li> Themed levels<br></li><li> Random level generation with varying sizes<br></li><li> Themed sudden death for each map<br></li><li> Basic fighting combo system<br></li><li> Throwable hazard ball that generates a random event</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discord Community Server</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617480/extras/1100fe509dec59f51538d1894249998a.avif?t=1627283233\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br>Whether it’s playing around or having a full-on competition, Fight party’s random map generation and weapons allows for a new battle to occur every round. Have a refreshed experience every round or pick and choose between what weapons you’d like to spawn.<br>However there can only be one winner.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 - 8 player split-screen multiplayer<br></li><li> Random items<br></li><li> Themed levels<br></li><li> Random level generation with varying sizes<br></li><li> Themed sudden death for each map<br></li><li> Basic fighting combo system<br></li><li> Throwable hazard ball that generates a random event</li></ul>",
